title: US agencies told to fire diversity staff; gender-neutral 'X' passports stopped
description: The Trump administration has directed federal agencies to terminate diversity programme staff within 60 days. title: Trump on Mount Rushmore? MAGA supporters push for his face on iconic monument

Representative Anna Paulina Luna is now preparing the necessary documentation to move forward with the proposal.
